As of mid-January, 2018, Kinetic Fit will no longer provide support updates to this version of Android. If you would like the most up-to-date version of the Fit app, you will need to upgrade your Android Operating System to Android Lollipop (5.0) or above. This app will still be usable on lower versions of Android, but support will be limited and there will be no further updates.
